{
  "video_id": "U_Q7axl4oXY",
  "title": "Making Education Accessible to Deaf Children | Nyle DiMarco | TEDxKlagenfurt",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Rhonda Jacobs Reviewer: Ellen Maloney"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 27411.0,
      "end_time": 29392.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to tell you a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 30199.0,
      "end_time": 35100.0,
      "text": "When I was 24, I found myself living in a small beach town"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 35100.0,
      "end_time": 37448.0,
      "text": "by the name of Naples, Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 38108.0,
      "end_time": 40189.0,
      "text": "I was looking for something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 40189.0,
      "end_time": 41967.0,
      "text": "I was 24."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 41967.0,
      "end_time": 43537.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m 29 now."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 44407.0,
      "end_time": 49830.0,
      "text": "And in that small coastal town, I was the only Deaf resident."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 50456.0,
      "end_time": 55578.0,
      "text": "In fact, the closest deaf person was a few hours away by car."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 56558.0,
      "end_time": 61389.0,
      "text": "And all of the friends and acquaintances that I had made could hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 61389.0,
      "end_time": 65331.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t mind though; I wanted something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 66238.0,
      "end_time": 68890.0,
      "text": "Lucky for me, Naples, Florida"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 68890.0,
      "end_time": 70740.0,
      "text": "is home to some of the U.S. Olympics volleyball team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 70740.0,
      "end_time": 72982.0,
      "text": "where they reside and train through the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 73390.0,
      "end_time": 77900.0,
      "text": "So I had a fantastic opportunity to play with them every day I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 77230.0,
      "end_time": 82290.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;d hit the court all the time, either indoors or out at the beach;"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 82290.0,
      "end_time": 83509.0,
      "text": "it was great."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 83509.0,
      "end_time": 86657.0,
      "text": "Lucky for them, I happen to be very good at volleyball."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 90838.0,
      "end_time": 93988.0,
      "text": "So one night after a great game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 93989.0,
      "end_time": 96889.0,
      "text": "a friend and I pull up some chairs by the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 96889.0,
      "end_time": 99844.0,
      "text": "to watch the sun go down and chat."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 102739.0,
      "end_time": 105927.0,
      "text": "And he looks over at me and he asks me a question"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 105927.0,
      "end_time": 108939.0,
      "text": "that completely blew me away."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 109420.0,
      "end_time": 113428.0,
      "text": "To be honest, in 24 years of my life, nobody had ever asked me."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 113999.0,
      "end_time": 116900.0,
      "text": "And his question was simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 116590.0,
      "end_time": 119469.0,
      "text": "\"Have you ever wished you could hear?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 119928.0,
      "end_time": 122109.0,
      "text": "I looked at him for a second and thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 122109.0,
      "end_time": 123946.0,
      "text": "Where did that come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 124247.0,
      "end_time": 127389.0,
      "text": "Then I took a moment and I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 127389.0,
      "end_time": 129700.0,
      "text": "while we had been sitting there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 129699.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132269.0,
      "text": "I could see waves coming in and crashing on the beach."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 132270.0,
      "end_time": 133749.0,
      "text": "He could hear that."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 134690.0,
      "end_time": 135738.0,
      "text": "Obviously, I couldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135739.0,
      "end_time": 138449.0,
      "text": "My entire world is completely silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138729.0,
      "end_time": 141880.0,
      "text": "To our left, people had taken over the court"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 141880.0,
      "end_time": 143936.0,
      "text": "and were playing volleyball, cheering each other on."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 144499.0,
      "end_time": 147668.0,
      "text": "To our right, a mother was playing and laughing with her baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 147669.0,
      "end_time": 148700.0,
      "text": "And behind us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148700.0,
      "end_time": 153528.0,
      "text": "cars and ATVs had passed by all day without me even noticing."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 155747.0,
      "end_time": 157819.0,
      "text": "So, I was quick to answer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 158118.0,
      "end_time": 161160.0,
      "text": "\"No, of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 161540.0,
      "end_time": 163667.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve never wished I could hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164101.0,
      "end_time": 167329.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve never wished that because I love who I am.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168339.0,
      "end_time": 172708.0,
      "text": "And you may be wondering, How do I love myself as a Deaf man?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 173148.0,
      "end_time": 176661.0,
      "text": "Well, first, I was born deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 177220.0,
      "end_time": 179738.0,
      "text": "My deafness shaped my childhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 179738.0,
      "end_time": 182289.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s all I&#39;ve ever known."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 183231.0,
      "end_time": 186249.0,
      "text": "So my perspective on life and my experience of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 186249.0,
      "end_time": 187847.0,
      "text": "is very different."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188310.0,
      "end_time": 190658.0,
      "text": "My outlook and my life has involved experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 190658.0,
      "end_time": 194279.0,
      "text": "that many of you have never had to encounter as hearing people."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195890.0,
      "end_time": 197899.0,
      "text": "My culture, something I embody and cherish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 197899.0,
      "end_time": 199910.0,
      "text": "has always been Deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 200250.0,
      "end_time": 202990.0,
      "text": "My perspective on life is completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 203549.0,
      "end_time": 206550.0,
      "text": "The experiences I&#39;ve had, something I hold most dear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 206550.0,
      "end_time": 209608.0,
      "text": "have taught me to love myself as a Deaf man."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 210619.0,
      "end_time": 212510.0,
      "text": "To illustrate that point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 213900.0,
      "end_time": 217750.0,
      "text": "if I were to walk into a job interview with a panel of hearing peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 218118.0,
      "end_time": 222910.0,
      "text": "and if I were to approach that meeting wishing that I could hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 223399.0,
      "end_time": 225836.0,
      "text": "wishing that I could speak like them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 225836.0,
      "end_time": 228410.0,
      "text": "and focusing on that imbalance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 229280.0,
      "end_time": 231298.0,
      "text": "do you think that I would do very well?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 231979.0,
      "end_time": 234120.0,
      "text": "Obviously not, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234965.0,
      "end_time": 237908.0,
      "text": "Because in the back of my mind I&#39;m focusing on the negative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 237908.0,
      "end_time": 240518.0,
      "text": "therefore creating a negative outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 240519.0,
      "end_time": 242769.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m certain I wouldn&#39;t get that job."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 243578.0,
      "end_time": 249407.0,
      "text": "But, if instead, I use my difference as an advantage and an asset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 249407.0,
      "end_time": 253410.0,
      "text": "I know that as a Deaf man I have so much to offer their company."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 253669.0,
      "end_time": 256800.0,
      "text": "My experiences growing up are much different from theirs."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 256800.0,
      "end_time": 260838.0,
      "text": "And knowing that allows me to approach the interview positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 260838.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263268.0,
      "text": "I can go into that meeting and confidently tell them"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 263268.0,
      "end_time": 265429.0,
      "text": "how they will benefit from hiring a Deaf man"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 265429.0,
      "end_time": 267489.0,
      "text": "for a multitude of reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 267489.0,
      "end_time": 272369.0,
      "text": "And I can walk out with that job because it&#39;s all about mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 273421.0,
      "end_time": 276978.0,
      "text": "So I say first and foremost to love yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 277653.0,
      "end_time": 282369.0,
      "text": "So as I mentioned, the first reason I love myself is my upbringing."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 282850.0,
      "end_time": 287129.0,
      "text": "But many of you may not know that I come from a rather large family."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 287600.0,
      "end_time": 290560.0,
      "text": "I have two brothers who are also Deaf"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 291100.0,
      "end_time": 293280.0,
      "text": "along with my parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 293509.0,
      "end_time": 295218.0,
      "text": "my grandparents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 295218.0,
      "end_time": 299431.0,
      "text": "and yes, even my great-grandparents as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 300240.0,
      "end_time": 303589.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the fourth generation in a beautiful family"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 303589.0,
      "end_time": 306551.0,
      "text": "with over 25 Deaf members."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 307978.0,
      "end_time": 311489.0,
      "text": "Born to Deaf parents who understood the Deaf experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 311489.0,
      "end_time": 313917.0,
      "text": "they knew exactly how to raise me."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 314339.0,
      "end_time": 316919.0,
      "text": "They knew how to provide me with the best opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 316919.0,
      "end_time": 318549.0,
      "text": "and to support me."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 319719.0,
      "end_time": 323349.0,
      "text": "From day one of my existence, my parents gave me language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 323350.0,
      "end_time": 325170.0,
      "text": "access to education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 325170.0,
      "end_time": 326690.0,
      "text": "and love."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 327849.0,
      "end_time": 330488.0,
      "text": "Growing up, my life was perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 330680.0,
      "end_time": 334538.0,
      "text": "Imagine, like many of you born to hearing parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 334538.0,
      "end_time": 337797.0,
      "text": "I never noticed barriers that simply weren&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 338239.0,
      "end_time": 340471.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure many of you felt your life was normal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 340471.0,
      "end_time": 342317.0,
      "text": "the same way that I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 342751.0,
      "end_time": 347477.0,
      "text": "Coming from a Deaf family, my world, in every way, was a utopia."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 353765.0,
      "end_time": 356568.0,
      "text": "When it came time for my parents to enroll me in school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 356568.0,
      "end_time": 359719.0,
      "text": "they already knew that I would go to the Deaf school."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 360700.0,
      "end_time": 363348.0,
      "text": "I would learn in an environment that was designed for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 363769.0,
      "end_time": 365938.0,
      "text": "At that time, all of my peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 365938.0,
      "end_time": 367658.0,
      "text": "and teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 367658.0,
      "end_time": 370450.0,
      "text": "and even the superintendent was Deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 371888.0,
      "end_time": 375289.0,
      "text": "So, I was still in my perfect world."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 375290.0,
      "end_time": 379200.0,
      "text": "I was in an environment where I could grow and where I could thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 379200.0,
      "end_time": 382219.0,
      "text": "And I had no problems; it was perfect for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 382449.0,
      "end_time": 385148.0,
      "text": "And many people don&#39;t believe that, but it&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 385148.0,
      "end_time": 390810.0,
      "text": "For me, the Deaf community, our world, was the perfect world for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390908.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "And I remember in the summer before fifth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 394879.0,
      "text": "I was ready to go back to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 394879.0,
      "end_time": 397538.0,
      "text": "and I asked my mom to go to a public school."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 397761.0,
      "end_time": 399129.0,
      "text": "She thought I was crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 399129.0,
      "end_time": 400919.0,
      "text": "She said, \"What?! No!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 400919.0,
      "end_time": 403580.0,
      "text": "Public school, it&#39;s all hearing kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 403580.0,
      "end_time": 406359.0,
      "text": "The Deaf school is a perfect fit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 406359.0,
      "end_time": 409479.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"No, I want to learn what those students are learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 409479.0,
      "end_time": 411579.0,
      "text": "I want to see what their classrooms are like."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 411579.0,
      "end_time": 413759.0,
      "text": "What are public school teachers like?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 414300.0,
      "end_time": 416308.0,
      "text": "So upon my insistence she enrolled me."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 416308.0,
      "end_time": 418548.0,
      "text": "And after two weeks of frustration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 418548.0,
      "end_time": 421488.0,
      "text": "I came home pleading to go back to the Deaf school."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 421781.0,
      "end_time": 426280.0,
      "text": "She listened very sympathetically and told me, \"Nope, too bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 426488.0,
      "end_time": 428188.0,
      "text": "I was floored."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 428488.0,
      "end_time": 430758.0,
      "text": "She told me I needed to stick it out for a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 430758.0,
      "end_time": 434370.0,
      "text": "because I needed to learn how to interact with my hearing peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 434380.0,
      "end_time": 436700.0,
      "text": "and that if I gave it a little patience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 436700.0,
      "end_time": 438597.0,
      "text": "I would learn so much about the world around me."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 438597.0,
      "end_time": 441578.0,
      "text": "Because the reality is the world is hearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 441950.0,
      "end_time": 444760.0,
      "text": "I was the only Deaf kid in the entire school."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 445490.0,
      "end_time": 448698.0,
      "text": "Of course, I always had hearing friends, but they could sign like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 449290.0,
      "end_time": 451880.0,
      "text": "So that year I gained a lot of insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 451880.0,
      "end_time": 454107.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t be involved in any of the school organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 454107.0,
      "end_time": 457329.0,
      "text": "My friends never learned enough sign to communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 457599.0,
      "end_time": 460869.0,
      "text": "And every time I tried to play a sport, I&#39;d get benched."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 460869.0,
      "end_time": 464800.0,
      "text": "The basketball coach told me a Deaf kid could never help the team win a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 464801.0,
      "end_time": 466640.0,
      "text": "And I was athletic."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 467831.0,
      "end_time": 471299.0,
      "text": "So after a year, I went back to the Deaf school"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 471299.0,
      "end_time": 474558.0,
      "text": "where I realized that&#39;s my home."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 474838.0,
      "end_time": 476489.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s my community."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476489.0,
      "end_time": 479340.0,
      "text": "And my community is where I can thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479800.0,
      "end_time": 481842.0,
      "text": "I got involved in the classroom again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 481842.0,
      "end_time": 483969.0,
      "text": "joined a bunch of school organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 483970.0,
      "end_time": 488800.0,
      "text": "and got back on the basketball team, where I helped win many games."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 488618.0,
      "end_time": 493530.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s without hesitation that I can say the Deaf community is in fact my home."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 494358.0,
      "end_time": 495750.0,
      "text": "After graduating high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 495750.0,
      "end_time": 498600.0,
      "text": "I was accepted into the only Deaf university in the world:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 498600.0,
      "end_time": 501370.0,
      "text": "Gallaudet University in Washington, D.C."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 501649.0,
      "end_time": 504139.0,
      "text": "It was there I gained my degree in mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 504139.0,
      "end_time": 506339.0,
      "text": "with the intention of becoming a better teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 506339.0,
      "end_time": 508212.0,
      "text": "than the ones I had growing up."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 508559.0,
      "end_time": 513850.0,
      "text": "Like many of you, I sat through some math teachers who seriously sucked."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 514111.0,
      "end_time": 515350.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 515350.0,
      "end_time": 517770.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be a good math teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 518590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522217.00000000006,
      "text": "But I also wanted to be a good role model for those students."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 524778.0,
      "end_time": 529350.0,
      "text": "So as time got closer to graduation, of course I was nervous."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 529599.0,
      "end_time": 532818.0,
      "text": "I started questioning if I had made the right decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 533720.0,
      "end_time": 536198.0,
      "text": "And I decided to get out -"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 536398.0,
      "end_time": 539328.0,
      "text": "to get out of my comfort zone and to travel the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 539580.0,
      "end_time": 542459.0,
      "text": "Since then, I&#39;ve been to over 43 countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 543710.0,
      "end_time": 545908.0,
      "text": "And the funny thing about when I travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 545908.0,
      "end_time": 548735.0,
      "text": "is that I&#39;m constantly meeting hearing people who say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 548735.0,
      "end_time": 552949.0,
      "text": "\"Nyle, you are so brave. How do you travel like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 552949.0,
      "end_time": 555320.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it hard to be Deaf and travel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 555321.0,
      "end_time": 557390.0,
      "text": "It looks impossible.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 558468.0,
      "end_time": 561670.0,
      "text": "And let me tell you, traveling as a Deaf person, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 561670.0,
      "end_time": 565193.0,
      "text": "is actually much easier than traveling for hearing people."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 565620.0,
      "end_time": 568640.0,
      "text": "Because sign language is something that gives me access"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 568640.0,
      "end_time": 570678.0,
      "text": "to a much larger world."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 573440.0,
      "end_time": 575398.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you one of my favorite stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 575398.0,
      "end_time": 579878.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, I was in south Sicily perusing a flea market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 579878.0,
      "end_time": 581969.0,
      "text": "when I walked into a butcher shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 582409.0,
      "end_time": 586990.0,
      "text": "and standing there is an American tourist trying to ask the butcher"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 586990.0,
      "end_time": 588841.0,
      "text": "where the meat he was slicing is sourced from."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 589180.0,
      "end_time": 594609.0,
      "text": "So the Sicilian man, speaking no English, is gesturing, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 594610.0,
      "end_time": 596619.0,
      "text": "And you know Italians gesture."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 596619.0,
      "end_time": 598928.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s trying to explain where the meat comes from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 598928.0,
      "end_time": 601289.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going right over the head of the tourist."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 601490.0,
      "end_time": 604409.0,
      "text": "So watching this very comical breakdown in conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 604409.0,
      "end_time": 606919.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m understanding everything perfectly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 607189.0,
      "end_time": 610358.0,
      "text": "so I pull out a paper and a pen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 610358.0,
      "end_time": 612377.0,
      "text": "and I translate what the butcher is saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 612378.0,
      "end_time": 614578.0,
      "text": "and I hand it over to the tourist and explain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 614578.0,
      "end_time": 616438.0,
      "text": "\"This is what he&#39;s trying to tell you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616438.0,
      "end_time": 619858.0,
      "text": "So there I am, the Deaf person translating for two hearing people."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 620108.0,
      "end_time": 624228.0,
      "text": "And in that situation, they&#39;re the ones disabled, not me."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624229.0,
      "end_time": 625679.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 628529.0,
      "end_time": 630268.0,
      "text": "While that story is ironic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 630268.0,
      "end_time": 633879.0,
      "text": "it happens so many times when I meet people in other countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 633879.0,
      "end_time": 636620.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m always amazed to meet locals in other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 636620.0,
      "end_time": 639649.0,
      "text": "and their ability to gesticulate and communicate with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 639649.0,
      "end_time": 641650.0,
      "text": "often quite easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 642930.0,
      "end_time": 646900.0,
      "text": "And I would always tell myself to visit the local Deaf schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 646900.0,
      "end_time": 649227.0,
      "text": "and to make time to meet Deaf locals."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 649738.0,
      "end_time": 652174.0,
      "text": "But with every new Deaf school that I saw,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 652174.0,
      "end_time": 655971.0,
      "text": "I was sad to see that their schools were in terrible condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 655971.0,
      "end_time": 659382.0,
      "text": "and their education was greatly lacking."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 659780.0,
      "end_time": 662768.0,
      "text": "Often, I just couldn&#39;t believe my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 663558.0,
      "end_time": 668128.0,
      "text": "When I would meet Deaf adults, I realized a common thread very quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 668128.0,
      "end_time": 671508.0,
      "text": "They either didn&#39;t have the same level of education I did"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 671508.0,
      "end_time": 675640.0,
      "text": "or their language was incomplete, making it hard to communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 676869.0,
      "end_time": 679689.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d often complain to me that the system had failed them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 679689.0,
      "end_time": 681860.0,
      "text": "and now they struggled to find work."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 682100.0,
      "end_time": 683358.0,
      "text": "And I kept asking myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 683358.0,
      "end_time": 687549.0,
      "text": "why is this happening, and why is this happening so often?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 687549.0,
      "end_time": 690270.0,
      "text": "Why am I somehow more fortunate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 690459.0,
      "end_time": 693469.0,
      "text": "Growing up, I thought every deaf person in the world was like me"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 693470.0,
      "end_time": 696980.0,
      "text": "and had the same opportunities that I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 697590.0,
      "end_time": 698838.0,
      "text": "So in returning to the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 698838.0,
      "end_time": 701240.0,
      "text": "I decided to do some research on the topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 701240.0,
      "end_time": 703500.0,
      "text": "And what I found shocked me."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 703668.0,
      "end_time": 706719.0,
      "text": "There are currently more than 70 million deaf people in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 706719.0,
      "end_time": 711120.0,
      "text": "with only two percent of them having access to education in sign languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 711439.0,
      "end_time": 714538.0,
      "text": "Which means millions upon millions of deaf children"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 714538.0,
      "end_time": 716882.0,
      "text": "not receiving the education they need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 716882.0,
      "end_time": 719390.0,
      "text": "also known as education deprivation."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 720520.0,
      "end_time": 724309.0,
      "text": "I also learned that over 75 percent of hearing parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 724309.0,
      "end_time": 727890.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t sign to communicate with their deaf children."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 727289.0,
      "end_time": 728858.0,
      "text": "Which is astonishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 728858.0,
      "end_time": 731617.0,
      "text": "Again, imagine millions and millions of deaf children"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 731618.0,
      "end_time": 734798.0,
      "text": "without an education, without a language."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 735848.0,
      "end_time": 738799.0,
      "text": "Those children without language and access to education"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 738799.0,
      "end_time": 740919.0,
      "text": "exhibit signs of brain damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 745200.0,
      "end_time": 746738.0,
      "text": "In my research, I also found"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 746738.0,
      "end_time": 749448.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m a part of an even smaller group."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 749828.0,
      "end_time": 753880.0,
      "text": "Ten percent of Deaf children come from Deaf parents like mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 753880.0,
      "end_time": 754833.0,
      "text": "Only 10 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 754833.0,
      "end_time": 756699.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m incredibly lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 756699.0,
      "end_time": 759640.0,
      "text": "I had access to language, an education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 759640.0,
      "end_time": 763161.0,
      "text": "and I had parents who loved me and put me on a path to success."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 763331.0,
      "end_time": 766310.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t be who I am today without any of those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 766949.0,
      "end_time": 769738.0,
      "text": "So it was clear to me that something needed to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 770878.0,
      "end_time": 773409.0,
      "text": "I got to work in setting up my own foundation -"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 773409.0,
      "end_time": 775258.0,
      "text": "the Nyle DiMarco Foundation -"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 775258.0,
      "end_time": 776999.0,
      "text": "with the goal of improving the lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 776999.0,
      "end_time": 779362.0,
      "text": "of millions of deaf people around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 779362.0,
      "end_time": 782968.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve since partnered with another Deaf organization in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 782969.0,
      "end_time": 784838.0,
      "text": "to introduce legislation -"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 784838.0,
      "end_time": 788368.0,
      "text": "a bill that requires all deaf children have access to language"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 788369.0,
      "end_time": 790670.0,
      "text": "between the ages of zero and five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 790670.0,
      "end_time": 793117.0,
      "text": "setting up benchmarks for their success."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 793329.0,
      "end_time": 794849.0,
      "text": "Because before the age of five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 794850.0,
      "end_time": 798400.0,
      "text": "children have the ability to acquire a foundation in language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 798400.0,
      "end_time": 801678.0,
      "text": "readying them for the classroom and for a successful life."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 801830.0,
      "end_time": 806139.0,
      "text": "After the age of five, that critical language acquisition window closes."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 807400.0,
      "end_time": 810868.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m working to give every deaf child in the world a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 810869.0,
      "end_time": 812210.0,
      "text": "filled with a rich language"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 812210.0,
      "end_time": 815259.0,
      "text": "and the opportunities I was lucky enough to receive."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 815568.0,
      "end_time": 817910.0,
      "text": "But the Deaf community cannot do it alone;"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 817910.0,
      "end_time": 820608.0,
      "text": "we need you to become our allies"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 820608.0,
      "end_time": 823777.0,
      "text": "and join us in making the world more knowledgeable."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 824159.0,
      "end_time": 828890.0,
      "text": "We need you to join us, to fight with us and for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 828890.0,
      "end_time": 832530.0,
      "text": "in the ongoing battle of affording children what they need to thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 836779.0,
      "end_time": 840821.0,
      "text": "So before I go, I want to teach you two very simple but important signs."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 841259.0,
      "end_time": 842959.0,
      "text": "The first is \"love.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 842959.0,
      "end_time": 844940.0,
      "text": "The second, \"yourself.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 845154.0,
      "end_time": 846149.0,
      "text": "Follow me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 846149.0,
      "end_time": 847639.0,
      "text": "Love"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 848397.0,
      "end_time": 849899.0,
      "text": "yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 850661.0,
      "end_time": 851958.0,
      "text": "Brilliant!"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 851958.0,
      "end_time": 854618.0,
      "text": "A-plusses all around!"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 854982.0,
      "end_time": 856540.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 856540.0,
      "end_time": 858228.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    }
  ]
}